import {
  SignPanelTitle,
  SignPanelTitleDesc,
  SignPanelButton,
  SignPanelInput,
  LinkGroups,
  SignPanelChange,
} from './SignPanelElements.js'

const SignIn = ({ setPanaleStatus }) => {
  return (
    <>
      <SignPanelTitle>登入</SignPanelTitle>
      <SignPanelTitleDesc>帳號</SignPanelTitleDesc>
      <SignPanelInput></SignPanelInput>
      <SignPanelTitleDesc>密碼</SignPanelTitleDesc>
      <SignPanelInput></SignPanelInput>
      <SignPanelButton>送出</SignPanelButton>
      <LinkGroups>
        <SignPanelChange onClick={setPanaleStatus('signup')}>登入</SignPanelChange>
        <SignPanelChange onClick={setPanaleStatus('forget')}>忘記密碼</SignPanelChange>
      </LinkGroups>
    </>
  )
}

export default SignIn
